      </a>
    </div>
    <ul class="grid list-none gap-3 p-0 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/data-ai/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-data" /></svg><span>Data &amp; AI</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/digital-workspace/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-workspace" /></svg><span>Digital Workspace</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/agile/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-agile" /></svg><span>Agile</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/cloud/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-cloud" /></svg><span>Cloud</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/devops/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-devops" /></svg><span>DevOps</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/finance/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-finance" /></svg><span>Finance</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/software-factory/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-code" /></svg><span>Software Factory</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/cybersecurity/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-shield" /></svg><span>Cybersecurity</span></a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/project-management/' | url }}" class="card card-interactive flex flex-col items-center gap-3 px-5 py-6 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue"><svg class="h-8 w-8 text-brand-gold-deep" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-pilotage" /></svg><span>Project management</span></a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- 3 entities, 1 governance --- #}
<section class="surface-gradient text-brand-ivory">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <h2 class="h2">3 expert entities, 1 unified governance</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl lead text-brand-ivory">
      The group brings together three complementary entities, ensuring strategic coherence, sector
      depth and execution continuity.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-10 grid list-none gap-6 p-0 md:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="card-on-dark p-8">
        <h3 class="h3 text-brand-gold">Navigacom</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Strategic information-system architecture.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-on-dark p-8">
        <h3 class="h3 text-brand-gold">Neofin Advisory</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Transformation of Finance and CIB business lines.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="card-on-dark p-8">
        <h3 class="h3 text-brand-gold">Meritis</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Technology engineering and delivery.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- Trusted by (client logos) --- #}
<section class="bg-brand-light">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 text-center md:py-16">
    <p class="eyebrow text-brand-gold-deep">They trust us</p>
    <h2 class="mt-3 h2 text-brand-charcoal">Large accounts in the most demanding sectors</h2>
    {% set clients = [["airbus","Airbus"],["air-france","Air France"],["axa","AXA"],["bnp-paribas","BNP Paribas"],["credit-agricole","Crédit Agricole"],["engie","ENGIE"],["essilor","Essilor"],["euronext","Euronext"],["groupama","Groupama"],["hsbc","HSBC"],["la-banque-postale","La Banque Postale"],["mediametrie","Médiamétrie"],["natixis","Natixis"],["orange","Orange"],["oticon-medical","Oticon Medical"],["parrot","Parrot"],["pierre-vacances","Pierre & Vacances"],["ratp","RATP"],["schneider-electric","Schneider Electric"],["societe-generale","Société Générale"],["sncf","SNCF"],["sodern","Sodern"]] %}
    <ul class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 items-center justify-items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-8 p-0 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6">
      {% for c in clients %}
      <li><img src="{{ ('/assets/images/clients/' + c[0] + '.webp') | url }}" alt="{{ c[1] }}" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain opacity-60 grayscale transition hover:opacity-100 hover:grayscale-0" /></li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- Impact-driven company (CSR / B Corp) --- #}
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="card-feature grid items-center gap-8 p-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:p-12">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow text-brand-gold">Impact-driven company</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 h2">Economic performance and positive impact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">
        B Corp certified, committed to workplace equality and responsible digital: we place people and
        the environment at the heart of our model.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="{{ '/en/meritis-csr/' | url }}" class="btn btn-primary shrink-0">
      Our CSR commitment
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- The Meritis blog --- #}
<section class="bg-brand-light">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2 text-brand-charcoal">The Meritis blog</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl lead text-brand-charcoal">Articles, insights and field experience from our consultants.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="{{ '/en/blog/' | url }}" class="link-arrow">All articles <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>
    <ul class="mt-10 grid list-none gap-6 p-0 md:grid-cols-3">
      {% for post in collections.blog_en %}{% if loop.index0 < 3 %}{% include "partials/card-blog.njk" %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- Join our teams --- #}
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
    <div>
      <h2 class="h2 text-brand-charcoal">Join our teams</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl lead text-brand-charcoal">Explore our opportunities and build your career at Meritis.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="{{ '/en/jobs/' | url }}" class="link-arrow">All jobs <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
  </div>
  <ul class="mt-10 grid list-none gap-6 p-0 md:grid-cols-3">
    {% for post in collections.jobs_en %}{% if loop.index0 < 3 %}{% include "partials/card-job.njk" %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

{% include "partials/cta-block.njk" %}
